718
00:48:32,000 --> 00:48:33,354
Fikirkan umur kita.

719
00:48:33,859 --> 00:48:35,494
Kenapa awak tak bawa kereta?

720
00:48:35,870 --> 00:48:38,894
Apa? Sebenarnya...

721
